{"tid":928868,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教畜們會唔會大題小做咗啲？【0、7被圈起重寫？】","createTime":"2018-12-05T07:18:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T07:35:43.000Z","uid":225464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c2a547905257909a8a8d6817c118d7759d0baff1","tid":928868,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T07:18:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181205/bkn-20181205133616544-1205_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181205%2Fbkn-20181205133616544-1205_00822_001.html&d=TKtuyFn5oTCSiI4%2BWKemeFeK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=f7e6456d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181205/bkn-20181205133616544-1205_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ES9UXzN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FES9UXzN.jpg&h=57d45420&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>0、7被圈起重寫　小一家長嘆無奈　到底錯喺邊？</strong><br />\n<br />\n教育局提供《香港小學學習字詞表》，供小學教師批改功課時作標準。惟除了中文字有規範，原來連數目字都要着重「字體」？<br />\n<br />\n有家長投稿至Facebook專頁「家長 Secrets」，指就讀小一的孩子做數學功業時，因「寫20，個0字冇圈埋」，因而被老師扣分。另一張照片中，「17」的「7」字疑因略為傾斜，亦被紅筆圈起改正。該家長慨嘆，學校一直很注重字體的寫法，「但估唔到數字都要」。<br />\n<br />\n有網民批評學校矯枉過正︰「考書法咩」、「到小三就發現寫字太靚做唔切卷」。有網民則認為，就讀小一、二時應執正字體︰「一旦習慣咗好難改」、「小一要學習運筆嘅意志」。你又點睇呢？"},{"pid":"7dd5c2f96d2d81f95ee6efc2eeed7861435add71","tid":928868,"uid":225464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T07:20:04.000Z","msg":"SORRY　係小題大做<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59c83c7a30e5d3acac5dc6bfa6484108302b430c","tid":928868,"uid":83094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T07:35:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}